        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer131282215" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer5832803271323509798">I wanted to give this book 4 stars originally just because it didn&apos;t have the ending I wanted, but in the end I couldn&apos;t justify that. I loved this book. It may not have had the happy ending I love, but it was so realistic because of that. Both Kit and John were excellent characters and I was able to connect with both. Some of the things Kit said made me stop to think, and I really felt for what John was going through on his journey to discover himself. Really a great read. </span>
  <span id="freeText5832803271323509798" style="display:none">I wanted to give this book 4 stars originally just because it didn't have the ending I wanted, but in the end I couldn't justify that. I loved this book. It may not have had the happy ending I love, but it was so realistic because of that. Both Kit and John were excellent characters and I was able to connect with both. Some of the things Kit said made me stop to think, and I really felt for what John was going through on his journey to discover himself. Really a great read. </span>
