<span id="freeTextContainer4363214484507629769">Eight Seconds is an amazing book. It is one of those that keeps the reader intrigued throughout the entire story. Of course it’s aimed at the teenage reader. Although the book’s central character is an 18-year-old guy girls too will be pulled into the story’s constantly changing relationships. His sense of self-discovery during his late teens is one of the most interesting elements to this story. </span>

